name: Sticker | Liazz (Glitter) | Rio 2022

This item commemorates the IEM Rio 2022 CS:GO Championship.

This glitter sticker was autographed by professional player John Tregillgas playing for Grayhound Gaming at the IEM Rio 2022 CS:GO Major Championship.
